query: UPDATE category SET name = COALESCE(?1, name), sort_order = COALESCE(?2, sort_order), is_kitchen_print_enabled = COALESCE(?3, is_kitchen_print_enabled), is_label_print_enabled = COALESCE(?4, is_label_print_enabled), is_virtual = COALESCE(?5, is_virtual), match_mode = COALESCE(?6, match_mode), is_display = COALESCE(?7, is_display), is_active = COALESCE(?8, is_active) WHERE id = ?9
